coordinatesText: Specify the coordinates of the sides of the bounding rectangle.
defaultText: Use the default extent as calculated from the input.
intersectionText: The extent in which all input features or rasters overlap.
layerText: Use the extent from a specific layer.
mapExtentText: Use the extent of the map displayed when running analysis.
setCoordinates: Set coordinates from current display extent
unionText: The combined extent of all input data.
useDifferentExtentForRA: Use a different processing extent for raster analysis
